flowchart TD
  reqNode[Gateway receives request]
  upstreamCallNode[Call upstream adapter]
  classifyNode{Failure class}

  reqNode --> upstreamCallNode
  upstreamCallNode --> classifyNode

  classifyNode -->|network timeout| unavailableNode[Return 503 upstream_unavailable]
  classifyNode -->|upstream 4xx| passthrough4xxNode[Passthrough status body]
  classifyNode -->|upstream 5xx| passthrough5xxNode[Passthrough status body]
  classifyNode -->|malformed upstream payload| protocolErrorNode[Return 502 or 500 gateway protocol error]

  unavailableNode --> obsNode[Emit logs traces metrics with correlation_id]
  passthrough4xxNode --> obsNode
  passthrough5xxNode --> obsNode
  protocolErrorNode --> obsNode

  obsNode --> doneNode[Response completed]
